story_teamrocket_01_15000/2401_1201_0100:
I forgot—we’re supposed to be Team
Rocket today!
story_teamrocket_01_15000/2401_1201_0300:
I see! I thought it was weird that we were seeing
so many Team Rocket members!
story_teamrocket_01_15000/2401_1201_0400:
I struck a deal with some of the more promising
members of Team Break.
story_teamrocket_01_15000/2401_1201_0500:
Perhaps we should continue our conversation
elsewhere, Professor Bellis.
story_teamrocket_01_15000/2401_1201_0700: This is bad! What do we do?
story_teamrocket_01_15000/2401_1201_0900:
Wait, I know that look in your eyes! Don’t
tell me—
story_teamrocket_01_15000/2401_1201_1000:
Whoa, hold on! You can’t let Snorlax Gigantamax
here! There’s not enough space—you’ll wreck the
whole place!
story_teamrocket_01_15000/2401_1201_1300: You won’t get away! Get them, Mewtwo!
story_teamrocket_01_15000/2401_1201_1400:
Wait! My memory stick! It has all my
research data!
story_teamrocket_01_15000/2401_1201_1500: We can’t go back now! We won’t make it in time!
story_teamrocket_01_15000/2401_1201_1600: Get out of here, everyone! Run!
